### Commerce Bank API — IntelliJ REST Client
### Install plugin: Settings → Plugins → search "REST Client" (by Jetbrains or community)
### Usage: click the green ▶ button next to any request to run it

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api

# After running "Employee Login" below, paste the returned token here:
@token = PASTE_TOKEN_HERE


###
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════
###  REFERENCE DATA (public)
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════

### Get all topics
GET {{baseUrl}}/topics

### Get all branches
GET {{baseUrl}}/branches

### Get branches for a specific topic (1 = Open an account)
GET {{baseUrl}}/branches?topicId=1

### Get all available time slots
GET {{baseUrl}}/appointments/time-slots

### Get booked slots for branch 1 on a specific date
GET {{baseUrl}}/appointments/slots?branchId=1&date=2026-06-01


###
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════
###  BOOKING (public)
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════

### Book a new appointment
POST {{baseUrl}}/appointments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "topicId": 1,
  "branchId": 1,
  "date": "2026-06-15",
  "time": "10:00",
  "firstName": "Jane",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "jane.doe@example.com",
  "phone": "555-123-4567"
}

### Book — should fail (slot already taken after first booking above)
POST {{baseUrl}}/appointments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "topicId": 1,
  "branchId": 1,
  "date": "2026-06-15",
  "time": "10:00",
  "firstName": "Another",
  "lastName": "Person",
  "email": "another@example.com",
  "phone": "555-999-0000"
}

### Book — should fail (invalid email)
POST {{baseUrl}}/appointments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "topicId": 1,
  "branchId": 1,
  "date": "2026-06-15",
  "time": "11:00",
  "firstName": "Bad",
  "lastName": "Email",
  "email": "not-an-email",
  "phone": "555-000-0000"
}


###
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════
###  EMPLOYEE AUTH
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════

### Staff login — returns { role: "staff", token: "..." }
### Copy the token value into @token above
POST {{baseUrl}}/employee/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "Mul3$!26"
}

### Admin login — use your admin password here
POST {{baseUrl}}/employee/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "YOUR_ADMIN_PASSWORD_HERE"
}

### Wrong password — should return 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/employee/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}


###
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════
###  ADMIN — APPOINTMENTS  (requires token)
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════

### Get all appointments
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/appointments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Search by name or email
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/appointments?search=jane
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Filter by date range
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/appointments?dateFrom=2026-06-01&dateTo=2026-06-30
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Reschedule an appointment — replace APPOINTMENT_ID with a real UUID
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/appointments/APPOINTMENT_ID/reschedule
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2026-06-20",
  "time": "14:00"
}

### Update status (confirmed | cancelled | completed | no_show | pending_action)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/appointments/APPOINTMENT_ID/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "completed"
}

### Save staff notes
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/appointments/APPOINTMENT_ID/notes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "staffNotes": "Customer called ahead to confirm."
}

### Cancel appointment (admin only)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/appointments/APPOINTMENT_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get appointment change history
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/appointments/APPOINTMENT_ID/history
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


###
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════
###  ADMIN — AUDIT LOG  (admin role only)
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════

### Get full audit log
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/audit
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Write an explicit audit entry
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/audit
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "appointment.status_change",
  "appointmentId": "APPOINTMENT_ID",
  "details": {
    "from": "confirmed",
    "to": "completed"
  }
}


###
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════
###  CHAT ASSISTANT  (public)
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════

### Send a chat message (streams SSE — requires CHAT_API_KEY to be set)
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messages": [
    { "role": "user", "content": "What branches are near Harrisonville?" }
  ]
}
